px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: SimSun;\">因为汇集了许多不同民族的人和文化，社会环境和道德观念变化很快，学生有可能沾染上一些不好的习惯</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: SimSun;\">语言能力可能无法达到母语水平，有可能影响升学</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: SimSun;\">学生自控能力较差，人生观尚未成熟，在这样没有约束的环境，很容易被错误的价值观引导</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: SimSun;\">大学</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: SimSun;\">好处：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: SimSun;\">大学出国心智成熟，</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: SimSun;\">价值观定型，不那么容易各种交集的文化所改变引导</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: S